file.content:
openapi: "3.0.3"
info:
  version: 1.0.0
  title: Swagger Petstore
  description: An API
  x-api-id: provider
  x-icon: pet
  contact:
    name: John
    url: https://john.no
    email: john@john.no
servers:
  - url: http://petstore.swagger.io/
tags:
  - name: Retail
    description: Retail pets tags
paths:
  /client-api/v1/pets:
    get:
      summary: List all pets
      operationId: listPets
      tags:
        - Retail
      responses:
        '200':
          description: A paged array of pets
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: "#/components/schemas/PetsResponse"
        default:
          description: unexpected error
          content:
            application/problem+json:
              schema:
                $ref: "#/components/schemas/Error"
components:
  schemas:
    Pet:
      type: object
      required:
        - id
        - name
      properties:
        id:
          type: string
          format: int64
          minLength: 1
          maxLength: 64
        name:
          type: string
          minLength: 0
          maxLength: 64
        tag:
          type: string
          minLength: 0
          maxLength: 12
    PetsResponse:
      type: object
      properties:
        pets:
          items:
            $ref: '#/components/schemas/Pet'
    Error:
      type: object
      required:
        - code
        - message
      properties:
        code:
          type: integer
          format: int32
          minimum: 0
          maximum: 12
        message:
          type: string
          minLength: 0
          maxLength: 64
